{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"text":" property is set to a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}]}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","title":"targetCoordinate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate","title":"targetCoordinate","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"location is being tracked.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/